data.description: If you're looking for some privacy in a great location this is the home for you! This unique A Frame has two bedrooms with a loft that can be used as a third bedroom or a bonus room and two full bathrooms. The large living room has a floor to ceiling stone veneer fireplace that's ran off gas. The outside is just as unique as the inside with a large deck and patio with a gazebo that has a metal roof. The outside also has a fully stocked pond with a dock to fish off of and a two car detached garage. Call today to schedule your private showing.
